\begin_layout Section
期望、平稳性和遍历性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
期望和随机过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
自协方差
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
平稳性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
遍历性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
举个例子：在时间序列中，一般来说，在计算期望时，我们往往能得到的总是时间维度上的平均，而不是真正意义上的总体的平均。对于一个平稳过程来说，时间平均是否最终收敛到
总体平均
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t})$
\end_inset

与遍历性有关。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
一个协方差平稳过程被称作是
\series bold
\bar under
关于均值遍历
\series default
\bar default
的：如果当
\begin_inset Formula $T\rightarrow\infty$
\end_inset

，时间平均依概率收敛与总体平均
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t})$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
一个过程，如果当j增大时，其自协方差
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{j}$
\end_inset

足够快地趋近于0，则该过程是遍历的
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
在第7章，我们会发现，如果一个协方差平稳过程的自协方差满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\gamma_{j}|<\infty\tag{3.1.15}
\]

\end_inset

则该过程关于均值是遍历的
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
类似的可以定义
\series bold
\bar under
关于二阶矩遍历
\series default
\bar default
：如果
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{T-j}\sum_{t=j+1}^{T}(Y_{t}-\mu)(Y_{t-j}-\mu)\overset{p}{\rightarrow}\gamma_{j}$
\end_inset

对于所有的j都成立。【第七章会给出二阶矩遍历性的充分条件】
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
特别的，当随机过程是一个高斯平稳过程时，条件(3.1.15)足以保证该过程的所有阶矩都是遍历的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
白噪声
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
移动平均过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
一阶移动平均过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=\mu+\varepsilon_{t}+\theta\varepsilon_{t-1}\tag{3.3.1}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\{\varepsilon_{t}\}$
\end_inset

是一个白噪声
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
矩
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t})=E(\mu+\varepsilon_{t}+\theta\varepsilon_{t-1})=\mu$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)^{2}=E(\varepsilon_{t}+\theta\varepsilon_{t-1})^{2}=(1+\theta^{2})\sigma^{2}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)(Y_{t-j}-\mu)=E(\varepsilon_{t}+\theta\varepsilon_{t-1})(\varepsilon_{t-j}+\theta\varepsilon_{t-1-j})=\begin{cases}
\theta\sigma^{2} & \text{，}j=1\\
0 & \text{，}j>1
\end{cases}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\gamma_{j}|=(1+\theta^{2})\sigma^{2}+|\theta\sigma^{2}|<\infty$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
q阶MA
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=\mu+\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...+\theta_{q}\varepsilon_{t-q}\tag{3.3.8}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\{\varepsilon_{t}\}$
\end_inset

是一个白噪声
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
矩
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E(Y_{t})=E(\mu+\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...+\theta_{q}\varepsilon_{t-q})=\mu
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E(Y_{t}-\mu)^{2}=E(\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...+\theta_{q}\varepsilon_{t-q})^{2}=(1+\theta_{1}^{2}+\theta_{2}^{2}+...+\theta_{q}^{2})\sigma^{2}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
E(Y_{t}-\mu)(Y_{t-j}-\mu) & =E(\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...+\theta_{q}\varepsilon_{t-q})(\varepsilon_{t-j}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1-j}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2-j}+...+\theta_{q}\varepsilon_{t-q-j})\\
 & =\begin{cases}
[\theta_{j}+\theta_{j+1}\theta_{1}+...+\theta_{q}\theta_{q-j}]\sigma^{2} & \text{，}j=1,2,...,q\\
0 & \text{，}j>q
\end{cases}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\gamma_{j}|=\sum_{j=0}^{q}|\gamma_{j}|<\infty$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
无限阶MA
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
Y_{t} & =\mu+\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...\\
 & =\mu+\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\theta_{j}\varepsilon_{t-j}\tag{3.3.13}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\{\varepsilon_{t}\}$
\end_inset

是一个白噪声
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
平稳的充分条件：
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\theta_{j}^{2}<\infty$
\end_inset

(平方可加)，或者更强一点：
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\theta_{j}|<\infty$
\end_inset

(绝对可加)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
矩
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t})=\underset{T\rightarrow\infty}{lim}E(\mu+\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...+\theta_{T}\varepsilon_{t-T})=\mu$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)^{2}=\underset{T\rightarrow\infty}{lim}E(\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...+\theta_{T}\varepsilon_{t-T})^{2}=\underset{T\rightarrow\infty}{lim}(1+\theta_{1}^{2}+\theta_{2}^{2}+...+\theta_{T}^{2})\sigma^{2}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)(Y_{t-j}-\mu)=\sigma^{2}(\theta_{j}\theta_{0}+\theta_{j+1}\theta_{1}+\theta_{j+2}\theta_{2}+...)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
一个系数绝对可加的
\begin_inset Formula $MA(\infty)$
\end_inset

过程的自协方差也是绝对可加的：
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\gamma_{j}|<\infty$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
自回归过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
一阶自回归过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
考虑过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=c+\phi Y_{t-1}+\varepsilon_{t}\tag{3.4.1}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\{\varepsilon_{t}\}$
\end_inset

是白噪声序列。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
从前面的差分方程可以知道：当
\begin_inset Formula $|\phi|\geq1$
\end_inset

时，不存在满足式(3.4.1)且具有有限方差的协方差平稳序列
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}$
\end_inset

。当
\begin_inset Formula $|\phi|<1$
\end_inset

时，存在一个满足(3.4.1)的协方差平稳过程，下面就是平稳解
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
Y_{t} & =(c+\varepsilon_{t})+\phi(c+\varepsilon_{t-1})+\phi^{2}(c+\varepsilon_{t-2})+...\\
 & =\frac{c}{1-\phi}+\varepsilon_{t}+\phi\varepsilon_{t-1}+\phi^{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+\phi^{3}\varepsilon_{t-3}+...\tag{3.4.2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

上式可以看作是一个
\begin_inset Formula $MA(\infty)$
\end_inset

，显然
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\theta_{j}|=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\phi|^{j}=\frac{1}{1-|\phi|}$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $|\phi|<1$
\end_inset

)【该条件不仅保证了
\begin_inset Formula $MA(\infty)$
\end_inset

表示的存在，也保证了
\begin_inset Formula $AR(1)$
\end_inset

是关于均值遍历的】
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
矩
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t})=\frac{c}{1-\phi}=\mu$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)^{2}=E(\varepsilon_{t}+\phi\varepsilon_{t-1}+\phi^{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+\phi^{3}\varepsilon_{t-3}+...)^{2}=(1+\phi^{2}+\phi^{4}+...)\sigma^{2}=\frac{\sigma^{2}}{1-\phi^{2}}=\gamma_{0}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)(Y_{t-j}-\mu)=E(\varepsilon_{t}+\phi\varepsilon_{t-1}+\phi^{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+\phi^{3}\varepsilon_{t-3}+...)(\varepsilon_{t-j}+\phi\varepsilon_{t-j-1}+\phi^{2}\varepsilon_{t-j-2}+\phi^{3}\varepsilon_{t-j-3}+...)=\frac{\phi^{j}}{1-\phi^{2}}\sigma^{2}=\phi^{j}\gamma_{0}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
对式(3.4.1)变形：
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}-\mu=\phi(Y_{t-1}-\mu)+\varepsilon_{t}$
\end_inset

，两边同时乘以
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t-1}-\mu$
\end_inset

并取期望可得：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{1}=\phi\gamma_{0}$
\end_inset

；如果两边同乘以
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t-j}-\mu$
\end_inset

(j>0)并取期望可得：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{j}=\phi\gamma_{j-1}$
\end_inset

，进一步可得到
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{j}=\phi\gamma_{0}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
二阶自回归过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
考虑过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=c+\phi_{1}Y_{t-1}+\phi_{2}Y_{t-2}+\varepsilon_{t}\tag{3.4.16}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\{\varepsilon_{t}\}$
\end_inset

是白噪声序列。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
写成滞后算子形式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2})Y_{t}=c+\varepsilon_{t}\tag{3.4.17}
\]

\end_inset

由差分方程的知识，当
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\phi_{1}z-\phi_{2}z^{2})=0$
\end_inset

的根落在单位圆之外是，式(3.4.16)才是协方差平稳的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(L)=(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2})^{-1}=\psi_{0}+\psi_{1}L+\psi_{2}L^{2}+...$
\end_inset

。在式(3.4.17)左右两边同时乘以
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(L)$
\end_inset

，得到
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}=\psi(L)c+\psi(L)\varepsilon_{t}$
\end_inset

。由此可以直接得到(
\series bold
\bar under
\color red
?
\series default
\bar default
\color inherit
)
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \psi(L)c=\frac{c}{1-\phi_{1}-\phi_{2}}\\
 & \sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\psi_{j}|<\infty\tag{3.4.22}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
矩
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t})=\frac{c}{1-\phi_{1}-\phi_{2}}=\mu$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)^{2}=E(Y_{t}-\mu)(\phi_{1}(Y_{t-1}-\mu)+\phi_{2}(Y_{t-2}-\mu)+\varepsilon_{t})=\phi_{1}\gamma_{1}+\phi_{2}\gamma_{2}+\sigma^{2}$
\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma_{0}=\phi_{1}\gamma_{1}+\phi_{2}\gamma_{2}+\sigma^{2}=\phi_{1}\rho_{1}\gamma_{0}+\phi_{2}\rho_{2}\gamma_{0}+\sigma^{2}\tag{3.4.30}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
又
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t}-\mu)(Y_{t-j}-\mu)=E(\phi_{1}(Y_{t-1}-\mu)+\phi_{2}(Y_{t-2}-\mu)+\varepsilon_{t})(Y_{t-j}-\mu)\Rightarrow\boldsymbol{\underline{\gamma_{j}=\phi_{1}\gamma_{j-1}+\phi_{2}\gamma_{j-2}}},j=1,2,3,...$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\Rightarrow\rho_{j}=\phi_{1}\rho_{j-1}+\phi_{2}\rho_{j-2},j=1,2,3,...$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
令j=1，得
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{1}=\frac{\phi_{1}}{1-\phi_{2}}$
\end_inset

；j=2，得
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{2}=\phi_{1}\rho_{1}+\phi_{2}$
\end_inset

，代入式(3.4.30)可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma_{0}=\frac{(1-\phi_{2})\sigma^{2}}{(1+\phi_{2})[(1-\phi_{2})^{2}-\phi_{1}^{2}]}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Subsection
p阶自回归过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
考虑过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=c+\phi_{1}Y_{t-1}+\phi_{2}Y_{t-2}+...+\phi_{p}Y_{t-p}+\varepsilon_{t}\tag{3.4.31}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\{\varepsilon_{t}\}$
\end_inset

是白噪声序列。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
写成滞后算子形式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p})Y_{t}=c+\varepsilon_{t}\tag{3.4.32}
\]

\end_inset

由差分方程的知识，当
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\phi_{1}z-\phi_{2}z^{2}...-\phi_{p}z^{p})=0$
\end_inset

的根落在单位圆之外是，式(3.4.32)才是协方差平稳的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(L)=(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p})^{-1}=\psi_{0}+\psi_{1}L+\psi_{2}L^{2}+...$
\end_inset

，与二阶自回归类似的，在协方差平稳的条件下，我们可以得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \mu=\frac{c}{1-\phi_{1}-...-\phi_{p}}\\
 & \sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\psi_{j}|<\infty\tag{3.4.34}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
矩
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E(Y_{t})=\frac{c}{1-\phi_{1}-...-\phi_{p}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{j}=\begin{cases}
\phi_{1}\gamma_{j-1}+\phi_{2}\gamma_{j-2}+...+\phi_{p}\gamma_{j-p} & \text{，}j=1,2,3,...\\
\phi_{1}\gamma_{1}+\phi_{2}\gamma_{2}+...+\phi_{p}\gamma_{p}+\sigma^{2} & \text{，}j=0
\end{cases}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
在上式两边同除以
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{0}$
\end_inset

可得
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{j}=\phi_{1}\rho_{j-1}+\phi_{2}\rho_{j-2}+...+\phi_{p}\rho_{j-p}$
\end_inset

，这就是
\begin_inset Formula $Yule-Walker$
\end_inset

方程
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Section
混合自回归移动平均过程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
考虑过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=c+\phi_{1}Y_{t-1}+\phi_{2}Y_{t-2}+...+\phi_{p}Y_{t-p}+\varepsilon_{t}+\theta_{1}\varepsilon_{t-1}+\theta_{2}\varepsilon_{t-2}+...+\theta_{q}\varepsilon_{t-q}\tag{3.5.1}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
滞后算子形式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p})Y_{t}=c+(1+\theta_{1}L+\theta_{2}L^{2}+...+\theta_{q}L^{q})\varepsilon_{t}\tag{3.5.2}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\phi_{1}z-\phi_{2}z^{2}...-\phi_{p}z^{p})=0$
\end_inset

的根落在单位圆之外，两边同乘以
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p})^{-1}$
\end_inset

可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=\mu+\psi(L)\varepsilon_{t}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \psi(L)=\frac{1+\theta_{1}L+\theta_{2}L^{2}+...+\theta_{q}L^{q}}{1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p}}\\
 & \sum_{j=0}^{\infty}|\psi_{j}|<\infty\\
 & \mu=\frac{c}{1-\phi_{1}-\phi_{2}-...-\phi_{p}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

因此，ARMA过程的平稳性完全取决于AR部分的参数
\begin_inset Formula $(\phi_{1},\phi_{2},...)$
\end_inset

，而与MA部分无关。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
与之前类似的，我们将ARMA写成均值离差形式，然后两边同乘以
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t-j}-\mu$
\end_inset

(j>q)并取期望可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma_{j}=\phi_{1}\gamma_{j-1}+\phi_{2}\gamma_{j-2}+...+\phi_{p}\gamma_{j-p}\,,\,j=q+1,q+2,...\tag{3.5.5}
\]

\end_inset

注意，当
\begin_inset Formula $j\leq q$
\end_inset

，由于
\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{j}\varepsilon_{t-j}$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t-j}$
\end_inset

之间存在相关关系，因此式(3.5.5)不适用。当
\begin_inset Formula $j>q$
\end_inset

且有相异的自回归根时，自协方差为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma_{j}=h_{1}\lambda_{1}^{j}+h_{2}\lambda_{2}^{j}+...+h_{p}\lambda_{p}^{j}\tag{3.5.6}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
注意，ARMA过程有过度参数化的可能，因为一个
\begin_inset Formula $ARMA(p,q)$
\end_inset

过程可以两端同乘以
\begin_inset Formula $1+\rho L$
\end_inset

而变成
\begin_inset Formula $ARMA(p+1,q+1)$
\end_inset

过程。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
自协方差生成函数
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
我们在研究时间序列是否平稳时，总会计算它的自协方差序列
\begin_inset Formula $\{\gamma_{j}\}_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

。如果这个序列是绝对可加的，那么一种概括这些协方差的方法是运用一个标量值函数，这就是我们接下来要探讨的自协方差生成函数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{Y}(z)=\sum_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}\gamma_{j}z^{j}\tag{3.6.1}
\]

\end_inset

前面提到的平稳
\begin_inset Formula $ARMA(p,q)$
\end_inset

过程可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}-\mu=\frac{1+\theta_{1}L+\theta_{2}L^{2}+...+\theta_{q}L^{q}}{1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p}}\varepsilon_{t}=\frac{\theta(L)}{\phi(L)}\varepsilon_{t}
\]

\end_inset

对应的自协方差生成函数可写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{Y}(z)=\frac{\sigma^{2}(1+\theta_{1}z+\theta_{2}z^{2}+...+\theta_{q}z^{q})(1+\theta_{1}z^{-1}+\theta_{2}z^{-2}+...+\theta_{q}z^{-q})}{(1-\phi_{1}z-\phi_{2}z^{2}-...-\phi_{p}z^{p})(1-\phi_{1}z^{-1}-\phi_{2}z^{-2}-...-\phi_{p}z^{-p})}=\sigma^{2}\frac{\theta(z)\cdot\theta(z^{-1})}{\phi(z)\cdot\phi(z^{-1})}\tag{3.6.10}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
一个例子：AR(1)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
滤子
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
有时候数据需要过滤，或者说在进行分析之前要对数据进行的一种特别处理，那么这种处理会对自协方差产生什么影响呢？
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定原始数据序列
\begin_inset Formula $\{Y_{t}\}$
\end_inset

是平稳的，令数据按照下述方式过滤
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
X_{t}=h(L)Y_{t}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & h(L)=\sum_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}h_{j}L^{j}\\
 & \sum_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}|h_{j}|<\infty
\end{align*}

\end_inset

则观测值可以由下式生成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
X_{t}=h(1)\mu+h(L)\frac{\theta(L)}{\phi(L)}\varepsilon_{t}\equiv\mu^{*}+\psi^{*}(L)\varepsilon_{t}
\]

\end_inset

而且可以证明与复合算子
\begin_inset Formula $\{\psi_{j}^{*}\}_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

有关的系数构成的序列是绝对可加的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
序列
\begin_inset Formula $\{X_{t}\}$
\end_inset

对应的自协方差生成函数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
g_{X}(z) & =\sigma^{2}\psi^{*}(z)\psi^{*}(z^{-1})\\
 & =\sigma^{2}h(z)\frac{\theta(z)}{\phi(z)}h(z^{-1})\frac{\theta(z^{-1})}{\phi(z^{-1})}\\
 & =h(z)h(z^{-1})g_{Y}(z)\tag{3.6.17}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

