E(\boldsymbol{Y_{1}Y_{1}}^{'}) & E(\boldsymbol{Y_{1}Y_{2}}^{'})\\
E(\boldsymbol{Y_{2}Y_{1}}^{'}) & E(\boldsymbol{Y_{2}Y_{2}}^{'})
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\boldsymbol{\Omega}_{11} & \boldsymbol{\Omega}_{12}\\
\boldsymbol{\Omega}_{21} & \boldsymbol{\Omega}_{22}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\Omega}$
\end_inset

左乘矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\boldsymbol{E}}_{1}$
\end_inset

，可使
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\Omega}$
\end_inset

的左下(
\begin_inset Formula $n_{2}\times n_{1}$
\end_inset

)矩阵块为
\series bold
0，
\series default
其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{\boldsymbol{E}}_{1}=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\boldsymbol{I}_{n_{1}} & 0\\
-\boldsymbol{\Omega}_{21}\boldsymbol{\Omega}_{11}^{-1} & \boldsymbol{I}_{n_{2}}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

如果对
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\Omega}$
\end_inset

左乘矩阵
