\[
\bar{\boldsymbol{A}}\equiv\bar{\boldsymbol{E}}_{1}^{-1}=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\boldsymbol{I}_{n_{1}} & 0\\
\boldsymbol{\Omega}_{21}\boldsymbol{\Omega}_{11}^{-1} & \boldsymbol{I}_{n_{2}}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

对
\series bold

\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\boldsymbol{D}}$
\end_inset


\series default
左乘
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\boldsymbol{A}}$
\end_inset

且右乘
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\boldsymbol{A}}'$
\end_inset

，结果为
